'''2014年[[埃及总统|埃及总统]]选举'''于2014年5月26日至28日举行。<ref name=ao30march>{{Cite news|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/97883/Egypt/Politics-/UPDATE--Egypts-presidential-elections-to-be-held-,.aspx|title=Egypt's presidential elections to be held 26, 27 May|agency=Ahram Online|date=30 March 2014|accessdate=30 March 2014|archive-date=2014-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403074338/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/97883/Egypt/Politics-/UPDATE--Egypts-presidential-elections-to-be-held-,.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>仅有两名候选人在最高选举委员会登记参选，即埃及前军方领导人[[阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西|阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西]]与左翼团体领导人萨巴希[[哈姆丁·萨巴希|哈姆丁·萨巴希]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Sisi, Sabahi to face off for Egyptian presidency|url=http://www.aawsat.net/2014/04/article55331446|newspaper=[[Asharq_Al-Awsat|Asharq Al-Awsat]]|date=21 April 2014|accessdate=23 April 2014|archive-date=2015-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207005402/http://www.aawsat.net/2014/04/article55331446|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Ex-army chief El-Sisi ahead of sole competitor Sabahi before presidential race|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/99504/Egypt/Politics-/Exarmy-chief-ElSisi-ahead-of-sole-competitor-Sabah.aspx|newspaper=[[Al_Ahram|Al Ahram]]|date=21 April 2014|accessdate=23 April 2014|archive-date=2014-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424071007/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/99504/Egypt/Politics-/Exarmy-chief-ElSisi-ahead-of-sole-competitor-Sabah.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

投票時間原定為2014年5月26日及27日，由於投票開始後投票率比預期低，當局在5月27日宣佈把投票時間延長一天至5月28日，期望提高投票率。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/05/27/us-egypt-election-idUSKBN0E70D720140527 |title=Egypt extends presidential election to help Sisi |publisher=Reuters |date=2014-05-27 |accessdate=2014-06-05 |archive-date=2014-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140602055607/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/05/27/us-egypt-election-idUSKBN0E70D720140527 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

6月3日，埃及最高选举委员会宣布，前军方领导人阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西在5月28日结束的总统选举中得票率达96.91%，战胜对手左翼政治家哈姆丁·萨巴希，以绝对优势赢得总统选举。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20140529-poll-egypt-sisi-landslide-win-president/|title=Egypt's Sisi set for landslide win in presidential vote|agency=France24|date=29 May 2014|accessdate=2 June 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140602034907/http://www.france24.com/en/20140529-poll-egypt-sisi-landslide-win-president/|archive-date=2014-06-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=ahram31may>{{Cite news|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/102610/Egypt/Politics-/ElSisi-faces-factious-agenda-after-landslide-victo.aspx|title=El-Sisi faces factious agenda after landslide victory|agency=Ahram Online|date=31 May 2014|accessdate=2 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140602173610/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/102610/Egypt/Politics-/ElSisi-faces-factious-agenda-after-landslide-victo.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>塞西在6月8日正式就任，成為第6任[[埃及總統|埃及總統]]。

== 背景 ==
这次总统选举是[[2013年埃及政变|2013年埃及政变]]和[[2012年至2013年埃及抗議活動|2013年6月埃及抗议活动]]及[[穆罕默德·穆尔西|穆罕默德·穆尔西]]总统被軍方領導人阿卜杜勒-法塔赫·塞西推翻，塞西實際掌權一年後，2014年1月埃及宪法全民公决之后举行的选举。临时总统[[阿德利·曼苏尔|阿德利·曼苏尔]]在2014年1月26日宣布将在议会选举之前举行总统选举。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/0/92617/Egypt/0/Egypt-to-hold-presidential-polls-first-Interim-pre.aspx|title=Egypt to hold presidential polls first: Interim president|publisher=Ahram Online|date=26 January 2014|accessdate=26 January 2014|archive-date=2014-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201185940/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/0/92617/Egypt/0/Egypt-to-hold-presidential-polls-first-Interim-pre.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>一个五人委员会将监督此次选举。<ref name=ao19jan>{{Cite news|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/News/91969.aspx|title=Egypt's newly-approved constitution to be followed by tackling key political laws|agency=Ahram Online|date=19 January 2014|accessdate=26 January 2014|archive-date=2014-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201154649/http://english.ahram.org.eg/News/91969.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>根据选举法，报名参选的最后期限是2月9日。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thecairopost.com/news/87268/politics/deadline-for-proposals-on-presidential-elections-draft-law-sunday|title=Deadline for proposals on presidential elections draft law Sunday|work=Cairo Post|date=9 February 2014|accessdate=10 February 2014|archive-date=2014-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209191021/http://thecairopost.com/news/87268/politics/deadline-for-proposals-on-presidential-elections-draft-law-sunday|dead-url=no}}</ref>总统选举法在3月8日颁布。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thecairopost.com/news/100966/elections-2/president-issues-presidential-elections-law|title=President issues presidential elections law|work=Cairo Post|date=8 March 2014|accessdate=8 March 2014|archive-date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502044451/http://thecairopost.com/news/100966/elections-2/president-issues-presidential-elections-law|dead-url=no}}</ref>

选举法规定，本次埃及总统选举候选人登记需满足3个条件：在15个省份收集至少2.5万名合法选民的签名支持；提供政府指定医疗机构出具的体检报告；支付2万埃镑（约合2900美元）的强制保险金。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140422/40004389_0.shtml|title=埃及总统选举仅两人申请 塞西获19万人签名支持|work=中新网|date=2014年4月22日|accessdate=2014年5月1日|archive-date=2014年5月2日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502002700/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140422/40004389_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

